{"about_the_game":"<strong>Bloody Heaven 2</strong> is a rogue-like action game with Rune-build feature. Based on 4 basic actions: <strong>light attack</strong>, <strong>heavy attack</strong>, <strong>skill</strong> and <strong>dodge </strong>,  you will assign runes in your weapon among slots of these 4 actions to build your battle style.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/\u5e7b\u5f71\u7b26\u6587.gif?t=1726210564\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/\u71c3\u70e7\u7b26\u6587.gif?t=1726210564\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/\u65e5\u6708\u7b26\u6587.gif?t=1726210564\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/\u95ea\u7535\u7b26\u6587.gif?t=1726210564\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Slash Into Hell</h2>As the Revenge Agent of Heaven, you will be able to use more than 3 classes, 12 types of weapon to slash among demons.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">4 Chapters, over 20 types of monsters</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/\u672a\u6807\u9898-1.png?t=1726210564\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Growing Power of Weapon</h2>Kill demons to collect gems, and then turn gems into rune inlays for your weapon. The runes could provide various of new abilities to contribute to your battle style.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/ezgif-5-1aca06d042.gif?t=1726210564\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Death Is Beginning</h2>If you die in a fight, the weapon is also lost with all the runes inlay. Your can start another challenge and if lucky enough, you could find the lost weapon.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Permanent Upgrade</h2>Win or lose, when you reborn back to heaven, all the gems you collect along the way will turn to dust. Make use of these dust to unlock permanent upgrade.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/\u5c40\u5916\u5347\u7ea7.png?t=1726210564\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"\u5b8c\u7f8e\u901a\u5173","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2816940/85d4b11fa2c1e23e280d386338082ffd09c713a3.jpg"}],"total":1},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1726210564","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1726210564","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1726210564","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1726210564","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<strong>Bloody Heaven 2</strong> is a rogue-like action game with Rune-build feature. Based on 4 basic actions: <strong>light attack</strong>, <strong>heavy attack</strong>, <strong>skill</strong> and <strong>dodge </strong>,  you will assign runes in your weapon among slots of these 4 actions to build your battle style.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/\u5e7b\u5f71\u7b26\u6587.gif?t=1726210564\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/\u71c3\u70e7\u7b26\u6587.gif?t=1726210564\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816940/extras/\u65e5\u6708\u7b26\u6587.gif?t=1726210564\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" sr